{#- Render a single patch's section to be appended at the bottom of an
    existing release-notes page. Mirrors the category formatting of
    `release-notes-page.njk` but emits NO frontmatter. The NPM badge is
    omitted when the per-version preamble already carries one (mirror of
    `hasPreambleNpmLink` in the full page template) so we don't render
    it twice. -#}
## v{{ version }}

{% if not hasPreambleNpmLink %}
📦 **NPM:** https://www.npmjs.com/package/@qvac/sdk/v/{{ version }}

{% endif %}
{% for p in preambles %}
{{ p.content }}

{% endfor %}
{% for section in overrides %}
### {{ section.heading }}

{{ section.content }}

{% endfor %}
{% for category in categories %}
### {{ category.name }}

{% for entry in category.packages %}
#### @qvac/{{ entry.pkg }}

{{ entry.content }}

{% endfor %}
{% endfor %}
